<p>On October 6, 2024, Teamwork Commerce employees around the world laced up their walking shoes and joined the global celebration of World Walking Day. From every time zone, our team walked as one, embracing the spirit of connection and community that defines both the event and our company values.</p>

<h2>More than a step count</h2>
<p>World Walking Day is about more than fitness alone. It's about fostering a sense of togetherness across borders. By taking part, our team supported global health and well-being while also strengthening our own bonds. Walking across cities, parks, and neighborhoods, we felt connected to each other and to the thousands of participants worldwide moving toward the same goal.</p>

<h2>Collaboration in motion</h2>
<p>Collaboration is at the heart of what we do at Teamwork Commerce, and events like World Walking Day are a reminder of the power of unity across a global team. Here's to more steps forward, together.</p>
